data.description: Immaculate updated ranch on full basement located on a cul-de-sac lot within walking distance to the community POOL! This home has been lovingly maintained and improved with fresh paint inside, some decorative wood accents, some new lighting, the basement floors was just installed in the finished area, new water heater and NEW ROOF! New Double Pane thermal insulated windows updated within the past few years. There is a screened in back porch for those fall evenings and a deck for summer cook outs. The main floor is at grade level entry with basement entry also possible from the driveway. The back yard is fenced in. The exterior has just been pressure washed and all of the porches and steps have a fresh coat of paint. 6 Miles from boat ramp at West Point lake.  You definitely want to see this one! Call today and set up your showing.
